metadata.name: iPay
metadata.description:
Pay is the god and patron of craftsmen, architects and engineers. Due to the nature of manual labor that he knows from top to bottom, Pay had acquired skin most relevant to his feelings.

As a major architect and craftsman, Pay had been present on most of the greatest achievements of mankind and as such represents group of the most hardworking and important people in our society.

Even tho Pay is constantly in cycle of making great things, he knows when to opt-out and acquire more skills for he is The Maker.
